variables.input:
fetch dt.entity.azure_subscription
| fields entity.name
| summarize subscriptions = collectDistinct(entity.name)
| expand subscriptions
| sort subscriptions asc

fetch dt.entity.azure_event_hub_namespace
| fields entity.name, subscription = accessible_by[dt.entity.azure_subscription]
| expand subscription
| fieldsAdd subscription = entityName(subscription, type:"dt.entity.azure_subscription")
| filter in(subscription, $Subscription)
| summarize namespaces = collectDistinct(entity.name)
| expand namespaces
| sort namespaces asc

fetch dt.entity.azure_event_hub
| fields eventHub = entity.name, namespace = belongs_to[dt.entity.azure_event_hub_namespace], subscription = accessible_by[dt.entity.azure_subscription]
| expand subscription
| fieldsAdd subscription = entityName(subscription, type:"dt.entity.azure_subscription")

| fieldsAdd namespace = entityName(namespace, type:"dt.entity.azure_event_hub_namespace")
| filter in(subscription, $Subscription) and
         in(namespace, $Namespace)
| summarize eventHubs = collectDistinct(eventHub)
| expand eventHubs
| sort eventHubs asc

fetch dt.entity.azure_event_hub_namespace
| fields entity.name, subscription = accessible_by[dt.entity.azure_subscription], region = belongs_to[dt.entity.azure_region]
| expand subscription
| fieldsAdd subscription = entityName(subscription, type:"dt.entity.azure_subscription")
| fieldsAdd region = entityName(region, type:"dt.entity.azure_region")
| filter in(subscription, $Subscription)
| summarize regions = collectDistinct(region)
| expand regions
| sort regions asc

fetch dt.entity.azure_event_hub_namespace
| fields entity.name, subscription = accessible_by[dt.entity.azure_subscription]
| expand subscription
| fieldsAdd subscription = entityName(subscription, type:"dt.entity.azure_subscription")
| filter in(subscription, $Subscription)
| fieldsAdd environment = splitString(entity.name, "-")
| fieldsAdd environment = arrayReverse(environment)
| parse toString(environment), """LD '", "' LD '", "' LD:environment PUNCT"""
| fields environment
| summarize environments = collectDistinct(environment)
| expand environments
| sort environments asc

1.title: Messages In
1.query:
timeseries Count = sum(dt.cloud.azure.event_hub.traffic.msg_in), 
           by: {dt.entity.azure_event_hub,
                azure.event_hub_namespace.name,
                azure.location, 
                azure.subscription
                }
| fieldsAdd EventHub = entityName(dt.entity.azure_event_hub)
| fieldsAdd Environment = splitString(azure.event_hub_namespace.name, "-")
| fieldsAdd Environment = arrayReverse(Environment)
| parse toString(Environment), """LD '", "' LD '", "' LD:Environment '", "' """
| filter in(azure.subscription, array($Subscription)) and
         in(azure.event_hub_namespace.name, array($Namespace)) and
         in(EventHub, array($EventHub)) and
         in(azure.location, array($Region)) and
         in(Environment, array($Environment))
| sort Count desc
| fields timeframe,
         interval,
         Count,
         EventHub,
         Namespace = azure.event_hub_namespace.name,
         Environment,
         Subscription = azure.subscription,
         Location = azure.location,
         dt.entity.azure_event_hub
| limit 50
